I"n<h1 id="nox">Nox</h1>

<p>Nox is a DIY differential drive robot which uses SLAM (gmapping) with a Kinect to navigate in its environment. It is powered by ROS running on a Raspberry Pi 3 Model B and an Arduino Mega controlling two DC motors with encoders.</p>

<p>Nox is a low-cost robot built with simple hardware, allowing for easy replication.</p>

